name: Chicken Feet #008
description: This dim sum dish is an adventurous one for many. I myself, never got into eating chicken feet because there are just too many bones to work through. It is a dish that is well known at dim sum and for adventurous foodies. It is said that chicken feet contains a lot of collagen and good for the skin! The cooked chicken feet is often covered in a tangy red sauce similar to that of sweet and sour sauce. Are you adventurous enough to eat this?
